===Etymology===
{{root|la|ine-pro|*bʰleh₃-}}
A root noun interpreted as an ''s''-stem noun, from {{der|la|itc-pro|*flōs}}, from {{der|la|ine-pro|*bʰleh₃-s||flower, blossom}}, from {{m|ine-pro|*bʰleh₃-||to bloom}}. Cognates include {{cog|grc|φύλλον}}, {{cog|got|sc=Goth|𐌱𐌻𐍉𐌼𐌰}} and {{cog|ang|blōstm}}, {{m|ang|blæd||leaf}} ({{cog|en|blossom}}, {{m|en|blade}}).

